## API Routes

### Webhooks

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/webhooks/github` | GitHub webhook handler |

### Projects

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/projects` | List all projects |
| POST | `/api/projects` | Create project (connect repo) |
| GET | `/api/projects/:id` | Get project details |
| PATCH | `/api/projects/:id` | Update project settings |
| DELETE | `/api/projects/:id` | Disconnect and delete project |

### Deployments

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/projects/:id/deployments` | List deployments |
| POST | `/api/projects/:id/deployments` | Trigger manual deployment |
| GET | `/api/projects/:id/deployments/:did` | Get deployment details |
| POST | `/api/projects/:id/deployments/:did/rollback` | Rollback to this deployment |
| GET | `/api/projects/:id/deployments/:did/logs` | Get build logs |
| WS | `/api/projects/:id/deployments/:did/logs/stream` | Stream build logs (WebSocket) |

### Environment Variables

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/projects/:id/env?scope=production` | List env vars |
| POST | `/api/projects/:id/env` | Create env var |
| PATCH | `/api/projects/:id/env/:varId` | Update env var |
| DELETE | `/api/projects/:id/env/:varId` | Delete env var |

### Databases

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/projects/:id/database` | Get database info |
| POST | `/api/projects/:id/database` | Create database |
| DELETE | `/api/projects/:id/database` | Delete database |

### Auth

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/auth/github` | Initiate GitHub OAuth |
| GET | `/api/auth/github/callback` | GitHub OAuth callback |
| POST | `/api/auth/logout` | Logout |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user |

### CLI

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/cli/deploy` | Trigger deployment from CLI |
| GET | `/api/cli/env/:projectId` | Download env vars (for `env pull`) |
| POST | `/api/cli/env/:projectId` | Upload env vars (for `env push`) |
